cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with facial image manipulation using deep learning techniques, specifically for makeup and de-makeup. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of adversarial networks, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel approach for disentangling content and style, which is a popular topic in the field of deep learning and could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves unsupervised learning, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which could be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics).
